sentences.sContent: In Brazil Nestlé sends its comestibles to local entrepreneurs who sell them to their neighbours.
sentences.sContent_eng: In Brazil Nestlé sends its comestibles to local entrepreneurs who sell them to their neighbours.
sentences.sCn: 在巴西，雀巢把食品运送到当地的企业家手中。 企业家再把食品卖给邻居。

sentences.sContent: But cultural shifts alone were not sufficient to exploit these calorie-rich comestibles. Our predecessors had to adapt genetically to them.
sentences.sContent_eng: But cultural shifts alone were not sufficient to exploit these calorie-rich comestibles. Our predecessors had to adapt genetically to them.
sentences.sCn: 不过要利用这些高热量食物，光是文化改变还不够，人类在遗传上也必须有所改变。

sentences.sContent: I beckoned him daily with a variety of comestibles, although sugar worked best.
sentences.sContent_eng: I beckoned him daily with a variety of comestibles, although sugar worked best.
sentences.sCn: 我每天都用各种食物来引诱它，不过糖最奏效了。
